## Captcha Module - English
captcha-enabled = ✅ Captcha verification enabled! New members must solve a captcha.
captcha-disabled = ❌ Captcha verification disabled.
captcha-mode-set = ✅ Captcha mode set to <b>{$mode}</b>.
captcha-mode-usage = ❌ Usage: /captchamode <math/text>
captcha-mode-invalid = ❌ Invalid mode. Use: math or text
captcha-timeout-set = ✅ Captcha timeout set to <b>{$timeout}</b> minutes.
captcha-timeout-usage = ❌ Usage: /captchatime <1-10>
captcha-timeout-invalid = ❌ Timeout must be between 1 and 10 minutes.
captcha-action-set = ✅ Captcha failure action set to <b>{$action}</b>.
captcha-action-usage = ❌ Usage: /captchaaction <kick/ban/mute>
captcha-action-invalid = ❌ Invalid action. Use: kick, ban, or mute
captcha-usage = ❌ Usage: /captcha <on/off>
captcha-settings = 🔐 <b>Captcha Settings</b>
captcha-verified = ✅ {$name} has been verified!
captcha-welcome = 🔐 <b>Captcha Verification</b>
captcha-solve-math = Solve: <b>{$question}</b> = ?
captcha-solve-text = Select the code: <code>{$code}</code>
captcha-time-info = ⏱ You have <b>{$timeout}</b> minute(s). Max <b>{$attempts}</b> attempts.
captcha-failed-timeout = ⏱ User {$user} failed to complete captcha in time. Action: <b>{$action}</b>
captcha-failed-attempts = ❌ User failed captcha after {$max} attempts. Action: <b>{$action}</b>
captcha-not-for-you = ❌ This captcha is not for you!
captcha-no-pending = ❌ No pending captcha found.
captcha-correct = ✅ Correct! Welcome!
captcha-wrong-answer = ❌ Wrong! {$remaining} attempt(s) remaining.
captcha-wrong-max = ❌ Too many wrong attempts!
captcha-need-admin = ❌ You need to be an admin to use this command.
